text: A HDB neighbourhood park that is modelled after constellations. Place was completely deserted when visited on Saturday 24 June 2023 late afternoon. Nice venue if you want peace and quiet whilst immersing yourself in nature.
A small neighbourhood park hidden next to West Spring Secondary School. It has a rooftop garden which have a nice view over to Stagmont Camp and Yew Tee plus the KJE.
Nice views from the park, a small yet complete neighbourhood park just next to a Secondary School. Hidden gem of this neighbourhood. I can imagine the fresh air in the morning!
very small park, able to cover it in less then 15mins.great view of the surrounding express way.
Very bad place very untidy and light was off or not working
